---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Red Teaming | Sheepdog Cyber Defense" description="Red teaming services for Texas businesses. Realistic attack simulations to test your detection and response capabilities.">
  <section>
    <h1>Red Teaming</h1>
    <p class="lead">We go beyond technical testing to simulate real adversaries. How well does your organization detect and respond to an attack?</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>What It Covers</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Full-scope attack simulations</li>
      <li>Multiple attack vectors (technical, social, physical)</li>
      <li>Detection and response testing</li>
      <li>Blue team evaluation</li>
      <li>Incident response assessment</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <p>Red teaming is about realism. We don't just tick boxes—we act like actual attackers. We'll use whatever means necessary (within scope) to achieve our objectives and see if your defenses catch us.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Deliverables</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>After-action report</li>
      <li>Timeline of attacker activities</li>
      <li>Detection gaps identified</li>
      <li>Response improvement recommendations</li>
      <li>Executive briefing</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Typical Timeline</h2>
    <p>Red team engagements typically run 2-4 weeks, depending on scope and objectives.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>What You'll Need</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Clear objectives and rules of engagement</li>
      <li>Point of contact for coordination</li>
      <li>Defined scope and boundaries</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <a href="/contact" class="btn">Request a Quote</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lead { font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 700px; }
  section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .cta { padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
</style>
